<!-- ══ VIEW: HOW TO ══ -->
<div class="view" id="v-howto">
  <div class="howto-header">
    <div class="howto-h1">How To Use <span>TSM Healthcare Command</span></div>
    <div class="howto-sub">Six steps to your first revenue recovery assessment — from onboarding to action in under 60 minutes.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="steps-grid">
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 01</div><div class="step-icon">🔗</div><div class="step-title">Connect Your Nodes</div><div class="step-desc">Grant read-only access to your EHR, practice management, or billing platform. TSM federates with Epic, Athena, eClinicalWorks, and 40+ systems via secure API.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: Start with your billing system — it's where the fastest recovery wins live.</div></div>
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 02</div><div class="step-icon">📂</div><div class="step-title">Upload Sample Documents</div><div class="step-desc">Use the Doc Uploader tab to drop in EOBs, remittance files, denial letters, contracts, or claims batches. Accepted formats: PDF, CSV, XLSX, CMS-1500, UB-04.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: A 30-day claims batch is ideal for a meaningful initial BNCA scan.</div></div>
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 03</div><div class="step-icon">🔍</div><div class="step-title">Deploy to Nodes</div><div class="step-desc">Select which nodes to query using the pill toggles, type or choose a query, and click DEPLOY. All selected nodes analyze in parallel using Groq llama-3.3-70b.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: Claims Integrity + COB nodes deliver the fastest measurable ROI.</div></div>
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 04</div><div class="step-icon">🧠</div><div class="step-title">Run Sovereign Strategist</div><div class="step-desc">After deploying, click SYNTHESIZE to have the HC-Strategist cross-reference all node outputs and produce a ranked BNCA action list with confidence scores.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: Use the Ask AI tab to drill deeper into any finding.</div></div>
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 05</div><div class="step-icon">📊</div><div class="step-title">Review the Dashboard</div><div class="step-desc">The Overview tab shows your 10-node health matrix in real time. Red and orange nodes are your highest-priority recovery opportunities. Click any node for full intel.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: A node below 75% almost always signals a recoverable leak of $20K+ per month.</div></div>
    <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">STEP 06</div><div class="step-icon">🚀</div><div class="step-title">Export & Execute</div><div class="step-desc">Download your Revenue Recovery Executive Summary as a PDF or share directly with your billing team. Schedule a 30-day re-audit to track improvement against baseline.</div><div class="step-tip">◌ TIP: Most clients see measurable improvement within the first 2-week sprint.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="howto-note"><div class="ni">ℹ️</div><div><strong style="color:var(--bright);font-family:var(--ui);letter-spacing:1px;">LIVE SYSTEM</strong> — Powered by Groq llama-3.3-70b-versatile via the SCHOOLS-3024 backend. All 10 HC nodes (wl-hc-medical through wl-hc-grants) are online. Deploy queries fire in parallel across the node mesh. No PHI is stored in the AI session.</div></div>
</div>

<!-- ══ VIEW: DOC UPLOADER ══ -->
<div class="view" id="v-upload">
  <div class="upload-header">
    <div class="upload-h1">Document <span>Uploader</span></div>
    <div class="upload-sub">Drop claims files, EOBs, contracts, or remittance data. The Strategist will scan and queue them for audit analysis.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="upload-layout">
    <div>
      <div class="drop-zone" id="drop-zone" onclick="document.getElementById('file-input').click()">
        <div class="drop-icon">📂</div>
        <div class="drop-title">Drop Files Here</div>
        <div class="drop-sub">or click to browse</div>
        <div class="drop-types"><span class="dtype">PDF</span><span class="dtype">CSV</span><span class="dtype">XLSX</span><span class="dtype">CMS-1500</span><span class="dtype">UB-04</span><span class="dtype">EOB</span><span class="dtype">TXT</span></div>
        <button class="upload-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation();document.getElementById('file-input').click()">Browse Files</button>
      </div>
      <input type="file" id="file-input" multiple accept=".pdf,.csv,.xlsx,.txt,.xls">
      <div class="analyze-row" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <button class="analyze-btn" id="analyze-btn" disabled onclick="analyzeFiles()">▶ Analyze with Strategist</button>
        <span class="analyze-note" id="analyze-note">Upload at least one file to begin analysis.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="file-queue">
      <div class="fq-title">Upload Queue</div>
      <div class="fq-empty" id="fq-empty">No files queued yet. Drop documents to begin.</div>
      <div id="fq-list"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

